stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> Init

    state "Initialization" as Init
    state "Forward Processing" as Forward
    state "Primary Validation" as Validation
    state "Refinement Processing" as Refinement
    state "Bottom-Up Completion" as BottomUp
    state "Top-Down Completion" as TopDown
    state "Termination" as Term

    Init --> Forward : initialize workflow

    Forward --> Validation : process level

    Validation --> Forward : threshold met<br/>children exist
    Validation --> BottomUp : threshold met<br/>terminal level
    Validation --> Refinement : validation failed<br/>refinement available
    Validation --> Term : validation failed<br/>unrecoverable

    Refinement --> Refinement : retry refinement
    Refinement --> Validation : refinement resolved
    Refinement --> Term : refinement exhausted

    BottomUp --> BottomUp : move upward<br/>in subtree
    BottomUp --> TopDown : reach root
    BottomUp --> Refinement : descendant failure<br/>refinement available
    BottomUp --> Term : unrecoverable failure

    TopDown --> TopDown : continue finalization
    TopDown --> Refinement : unresolved nodes<br/>refinement available
    TopDown --> Term : unrecoverable failure
    TopDown --> Term : successful completion
